film, they express disappointment with the dull characters, lack of depth, and unanswered questions in the plot. They also suggest that the movie might be enjoyable for those who are new to the anime genre, but they recommend borrowing or buying it at a low price instead of investing in it. Overall, the reviewer expresses dissatisfaction with the film and implies that they had higher expectations for it based on other anime works."}
