The customer made a payment with a gift card that had a balance of $10, so the remaining amount to be paid is $11.92 - $10 = $1.92.\n- The total amount spent by the customer is $1.92.\nSince the total amount spent by the customer is less than the limit of $20 for their shopping trip, they were able to make all the purchases they intended to make."}
