e the trained model weights and architecture to a file. Then, upload these files to a storage bucket in your GCP project. Finally, you can use Google Cloud functions or other deployment methods to expose an API endpoint that accepts movie reviews and returns the predicted sentiment (positive or negative) using the deployed LSTM model.\n\nBy following these steps, you will be able to deploy an LSTM AI model on Google Cloud that can classify movie reviews as positive or negative."}
