ed many reports of bad behavior, like mean messages, harassment, and even criminal damage towards these members. Some people worry that members of Parliament are facing more mean behavior, especially on the internet. One female member of Parliament received threats and a very scary picture in the mail. Another member said that almost every member of Parliament has experienced some kind of mean or threatening behavior. The article suggests that this might be connected to big decisions, like Brexit, that people have strong feelings about."}
