up A4 × C3, or one of the nine non-abelian groups of order 36:\n\n1. Cyclic group C36\n2. C6 × C6 (non-abelian)\n3. C3 ⋊ C12 and C4 ⋊ C9 (non-abelian)\n4. C3 × C3 × C4 (A4 × C3)\n5. C2 ⋊ (C3 × C6) and C6 ⋊ (C2 × C3) (non-abelian)"}
